{
  "chapter": 21,
  "chapter_summary": "第二十一回「帮主夫人」。秋灵素向楚留香讲述往事：天枫十四郎带伤挑战任慈，被竹节杖击中而死，临终托孤。秋灵素推测天枫十四郎的遗孤就是南宫灵——这解释了任慈为何明知南宫灵害己却仍容忍。楚留香请求一睹秋灵素真容，黑纱掀起后，露出的是一张被毁的狰狞面目。秋灵素平静地讲述了二十年前石观音因嫉妒她的美貌，以魔镜之喻威逼她自毁容貌的经过。秋灵素为将美丽永留人间，请孙学圃绘制四幅画像，而后毁容、疯狂中挖去孙学圃眼珠。毁容后任慈不离不弃，日日陪伴，以无限包容和深情融化了秋灵素，使她明白世上最仁慈的人就是任慈。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "text": "两个什么字?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "speaker_name": "秋灵素",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "只说了'来吧'这两个字，便闭口不语，任慈见他如此狂傲，也不觉动了火气，所以也就懒得和他说话。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "text": "任帮主可用了兵刃?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "speaker_name": "秋灵素",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "任慈使的，正是历代丐帮帮主传统的兵刃竹节杖，也就是俗称'打狗棒'的，两人交手不到十招，任慈已将天枫十四郎掌中剑震飞，一杖打在他胸口上，天枫十四郎立刻口吐鲜血而倒。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "text": "天枫十四郎挟技而来，怎会如此不济?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "speaker_name": "秋灵素",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "任慈当时本也奇怪，后来才知道，原来任慈并非这天枫十四郎第一个挑战的人，就在同一天里，天枫十四郎已和别人决斗过一场，而且已受到很重的内伤，他若肯说出来，任慈自然绝不会乘人之危和他动手，但他却怕自己说出后，别人会以为他有了怯意，所以只说了'来吧'两个宇，对自己的伤势，竟是始终绝口不提，任慈却以为他是生性狂傲，不屑与别人说话哩!",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "speaker_name": "秋灵素",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他受的内伤本已极重，再加上任慈的一棒，内外伤一齐发作，铁人也禁受不起，当天就不支而死，直到临死时，也没有说一句示弱的话，更没有丝毫埋怨任慈之意，只说他能死在战场上，已算不虚此生。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "text": "这天枫十四郎既不肯示弱，更不肯失信，明知必死，还是在那里等着应战，当真不愧是天下少见的英雄铁汉。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "speaker_name": "秋灵素",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "这大概也就是东瀛武士们，引以为荣的武道精神。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "text": "无论如何，这种人总是值得别人钦佩的，也难怪任老帮主直到二十年后，仍然时常惦念着他。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "speaker_name": "秋灵素",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "天枫十四郎之死，责任虽不在任慈，但任慈却终生歉疚在心，总是说只要自己那天稍微留意些，便不难瞧出天枫十四郎已受了伤的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "text": "在任老帮主之前击伤他的人是谁呢?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "speaker_name": "秋灵素",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "任慈始终没有提起此事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这人想必和任老帮主一样，不好虚名，是以他和天枫十四郎那一战，直到如今，还没有人知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "speaker_name": "秋灵素",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我将这故事告诉你，并非全无原因。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "text": "还有什么原因?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "speaker_name": "秋灵素",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "天枫十四郎临死时，曾经托付任慈一件事，但无论如何我去问任慈，他总是不肯将这件事说出来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "text": "任老帮主为何将这件事看得如此秘密?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "speaker_name": "秋灵素",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "此事我本也茫然不知，到后来却猜出了一些。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "text": "哦!",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "speaker_name": "秋灵素",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "任慈每见到南宫灵后，总要想起天枫十四郎，为之唏嘘感慨终日，到后来他虽明知南宫灵害了他，但仍不肯有丝毫伤害到南宫灵，总说他本对不起南宫灵，但他将南宫灵扶养成人，又会有什么事对不起他呢?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "text": "你的意思莫非是说，南宫灵便是那天枫十四郎的遗孤么?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "speaker_name": "秋灵素",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "正是如此。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "text": "不错!任老帮主始终不肯说出那件事，为的正是生怕南宫灵知道自己身世的秘密后，会生出偏激之心。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "speaker_name": "秋灵素",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你总算也能了解任慈的苦心，他那时简直已将南宫灵视如自己的儿子，自然不愿南宫灵知道他便是杀死自己亲生父亲的人，他一生行事素来磊落，却还是有件不可告人的秘密，心中痛苦，可想而知。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "text": "但无论他如何隐瞒，最后害死他的，竟终还是南宫灵，他在二十年前无心做错了件事，却在二十年后付出了自己的生命。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "speaker_name": "秋灵素",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "这若真是苍天要他付出的代价，苍天也未免太不公平。",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "text": "但南宫灵是否也已知道这件事呢?那神秘的凶手，是否也和天枫十四郎有什么关系?否则他又怎能学会东瀛武士的忍术秘技?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "speaker_name": "秋灵素",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "这些秘密，都有待你去发掘了，我所知道的秘密，已全部告诉了你，你……你可以走了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "text": "在下还想请求夫人一件事。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "speaker_name": "秋灵素",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "还有什么事?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "text": "不知夫人可否掀开面纱，让在下能一睹夫人之丰采?",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "speaker_name": "秋灵素",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你真要瞧瞧我么?",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "text": "在下有此愿望，已非一日。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "speaker_name": "秋灵素",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "二十年来，你是能瞧见我真面目的第二个人。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "text": "能瞧见夫人面目的，只有两个人?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "speaker_name": "秋灵素",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "不错，只有两个人，你，任慈……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "speaker_name": "秋灵素",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你现在满意了么?",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "text": "在下……在下实在不知道……",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "speaker_name": "秋灵素",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你现在总已该知道，为什么只有任慈和你瞧过这张脸，只因我的脸早已被毁了，我想，世上绝没有一个女人会愿意被别人瞧见这副样子的，是么?",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "text": "在下实在该死，在下为什么要逼夫人……",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "speaker_name": "秋灵素",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你没有逼我，是我愿意让你瞧的。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "speaker_name": "秋灵素",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "只可惜你迟来了二十年，我竟不能让楚留香瞧见我二十年前的容貌，这在你固然是件遗憾，我又何尝不算得遗憾呢?",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "text": "无论夫人容貌变得怎样，夫人的风姿，仍是天下无双，在下能见到夫人的风仪，已是三生有幸了。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "speaker_name": "秋灵素",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你不必安慰我，因为我并不难受，我容貌被毁的这二十年，才是我一生中最幸福的日子。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "speaker_name": "秋灵素",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我甚至还有些感激那将我容貌毁去的人，若不是她，我又怎能享受到二十年宁静幸福的岁月?",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "text": "却不知那人是谁?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "speaker_name": "秋灵素",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你可听过'石观音'这个名字?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "text": "石观音?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "speaker_name": "秋灵素",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你自然知道这个名字，她本是这世上武功最高，心肠最冷的女人。现在，她只怕也可算是这世上最美的女人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "text": "她……她又和夫人有什么仇恨?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "speaker_name": "秋灵素",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "没有仇恨，她甚至只不过见了我一面而已。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "text": "那么她为什么……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "speaker_name": "秋灵素",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在江湖传说中，据说她有一面魔镜，她每天都要问这面镜子……'谁是天下最美丽的女人?'",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "text": "这面镜子每次都说她是世上最美丽的女人?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "speaker_name": "秋灵素",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "不错，直到有一天，这魔镜的回答忽然改变了，它竟说我……说秋灵素才是世上最美丽的女人。而我的灾祸，也就在这时开始了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "text": "所以，她就来找夫人?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "speaker_name": "秋灵素",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "她找到我时，曾经动也不动地，对我凝注了两个时辰，在这两个时辰里她几乎连眼睛都没有眨过。然后忽然问我，说道：'你是愿意我杀死你，还是愿意毁去自己的容貌?'……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "text": "这句话问得当真可笑。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "speaker_name": "秋灵素",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "但当时我却丝毫不觉可笑，我只觉手脚发冷，一句话也说不出来，她又瞧了我半晌，忽然转过身，说：'三个月后，我当再来，那时我若瞧见你还是这样子，我就杀了你。'",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "speaker_name": "秋灵素",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她在桌上留下个瓶子，又说：'我让你再保留三个月的美丽，你当然知道好生珍惜'。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "text": "她既然已走了，夫人为何不……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "speaker_name": "秋灵素",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "石观音若要杀一个人时，没有人能逃得掉的，我亲眼瞧见她的武功，那时，我也不想死。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "text": "世上焉有真的想死的人!",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "speaker_name": "秋灵素",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那时，我还年轻，对生命真是充满了热爱，我想，我纵不再美丽，但能活下去，总比死了的好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "speaker_name": "秋灵素",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我又想，至少我还有三个月的美丽，我自然该好好珍惜，那么，在这三个月里，我该做些什么事呢?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "text": "于是夫人就想将这美丽永远保存在人们心中，于是就找到了天下最负盛名的人像画家孙学圃。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "speaker_name": "秋灵素",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你……你已知道了?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "text": "在下已见过了孙先生。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "speaker_name": "秋灵素",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那时我做事实在太任性……就在画成的那天晚上，三个月的期限已到，石观音向来都是最准时的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "text": "所以夫人就在那天晚上，毁去了自己的容貌。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "speaker_name": "秋灵素",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "石观音留下的那小瓶子里，就是一瓶比火还烈，最灼人的药水。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "text": "夫人不愿意孙先生醒来后，瞧见夫人容貌已毁，所以就……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "speaker_name": "秋灵素",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我将那瓶药水淋在脸上后，神智已几乎疯狂，所以……所以才会做出那种事，我……我……",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "text": "直到现在，在下才知道夫人为何要对孙先生如此，为何要画那四幅画，以前我们对夫人的用意，完全都猜错了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "speaker_name": "秋灵素",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "无论我为的是什么，我做出那种事来，你都不会原谅我的，是么?",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "text": "在下只知道现在的任夫人，是世上最温和，最仁慈的女人，至于以前那秋灵素是怎样的，在下既不知道，也不关心。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "speaker_name": "秋灵素",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "这二十年来，我的确改变了许多，你当然也可猜得出，是谁令我改变的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "text": "任老帮主。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "speaker_name": "秋灵素",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我在疯狂中挖去孙学圃的眼珠后，自己也昏迷不醒，醒来时整个头都已被包扎起来，此后我便在黑暗中生活了几个月，那时我真不知有多么的感激素心大师，若不是她照顾我，我怎能活下去?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "speaker_name": "秋灵素",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但等到我重见光明时才知道，时时刻刻在身旁照顾我的，竟不是素心，而是任慈。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "text": "所以夫人就将那感激之心，转给任老帮主?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "speaker_name": "秋灵素",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那时我非但没有感激他，反而恨他!",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "text": "恨?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "speaker_name": "秋灵素",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我见到任慈时，也见到了自己的脸，我见到这张脸，才知道我已没法子活下去，我失去了容貌，也就等于失去了生命……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "speaker_name": "秋灵素",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那时我心里既悲哀，又愤怒，更恨任慈为什么要在这种时候见到我，我疯狂般将他赶了出去。",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "text": "夫人那时的心情，在下倒也能了解几分。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "speaker_name": "秋灵素",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那么你也该知道，像任慈这种人，是赶不走的，第二天早上，他又来了，我又赶走了他……",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "text": "但第三天早上，他还是来了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "speaker_name": "秋灵素",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "他天天来，我天天赶，我用尽了世上所有恶毒的话骂他，甚至打他，但他还是一早就来了……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "speaker_name": "秋灵素",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你知道，那时他已是丐帮的帮主，他本不必对一个既丑怪，又凶狠的女人如此忍耐的，你现在瞧着我的脸，也该知道，除了任慈之外，世上绝不会再有别的男人对我如此忍受的。除非我真的是个死人，否则又怎会不被他感动呢?",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "text": "这只因任老帮主爱的本不是失去的美丽，而是夫人的……灵魂，他只知道人人的容貌虽然改变，但灵魂却不会改变的。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "speaker_name": "秋灵素",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "只可惜任慈活着时没有认识你，否则，你一定会成为他的好朋友……只不过，你对他的了解还不够，你还是猜错了。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "text": "哦?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "speaker_name": "秋灵素",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "在那时以前，我和任慈只不过见过两面而已，他又怎会对我如此痴情?何况，那时我美丽的只是躯壳，我的灵魂本是丑恶的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "text": "有时人们也会一见钟情，情深入骨的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "speaker_name": "秋灵素",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "无论如何，这总不是主要的原因，主要的原因是他知道一个女人容貌被毁后的痛苦，他也知道惟有情感才能令这种痛苦减轻，所以他决定牺牲自己，来陪伴我，安慰我一生。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ling_su",
      "speaker_name": "秋灵素",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我早已说过，他是世上最仁慈的人。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    }
  ],
